00:00:20.934 --> 00:00:23.300
NARRATOR: Some families
dress a daughter as a boy

00:00:23.300 --> 00:00:26.166
because they don't
have any sons.

00:00:26.166 --> 00:00:28.166
bacha posh can be
a sort of good luck

00:00:28.166 --> 00:00:29.533
charm for future pregnancies.

00:00:29.533 --> 00:00:30.867
[music playing]

00:00:49.633 --> 00:00:53.667
NARRATOR: Women in Afghanistan
can't go outside unaccompanied.

00:00:53.667 --> 00:00:56.266
Abass helps her mother
by going to the market

00:00:56.266 --> 00:00:57.767
and running errands.

00:00:57.767 --> 00:00:58.934
She also goes to school.

00:00:58.934 --> 00:00:59.734
[music playing]

00:01:15.867 --> 00:01:18.600
NARRATOR: Families often
keep girls and women at home.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:26.667
